<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:08:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>东京遭遇地震，无海啸预警</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tokyo-rattled-by-quake-no-tsunami-warning/articleshow/108664637.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108664637.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周五早上，东京附近发生 5.3 级地震，东京建筑物摇晃，紧急电话警报响起，但没有发布海啸警报。今年元旦发生的 7.5 级地震就证明了这一点，这次地震袭击了能登半岛，造成 230 多人死亡，其中许多人是因旧建筑倒塌而丧生。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tokyo-rattled-by-quake-no-tsunami-warning/articleshow/108664637.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国年轻人通过玩彩票缓解对经济的焦虑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/young-chinese-ease-their-angst-over-economy-by-playing-lottery/articleshow/108664027.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108664027.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;吸引年轻顾客参与国家批准的彩票游戏的举措非常成功。去年，销售额飙升至前所未有的 5800 亿元人民币（806 亿美元）。人们注意到彩票参与者的人口结构发生了重大变化，其中超过五分之四的人年龄在 18-34 岁之间，与 2020 年的一半多一点相比显着增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/young-chinese-ease-their-angst-over-economy-by-playing-lottery/articleshow/108664027.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦正义运动领导人哈马德·阿扎尔辞去旁遮普省党主席兼总书记职务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-leader-hammad-azhar-steps-down-as-punjabs-party-president-general-secretary/articleshow/108663335.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108663335.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦正义运动党领导人哈马德·阿扎尔以法律问题和绩效问题为由，辞去旁遮普省总书记和代理主席职务。他将自己的责任归咎于 PTI 创始人伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan)，并面临来自“法西斯政权”的挑战。爱资哈尔自 2023 年 5 月起秘密为该党工作，被控 42 起案件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:03:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-leader-hammad-azhar-steps-down-as-punjabs-party-president-general-secretary/articleshow/108663335.cms</guid></item><item><title>“阿鲁纳恰尔邦是印度的一部分”：中印紧张局势加剧之际美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/arunachal-pradesh-part-of-india-us-amid-rising-india-china-tensions/articleshow/108662795.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108662795.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务院周三表示，美国政府承认阿鲁纳恰尔邦是印度领土的一部分，并“强烈”谴责任何沿实际控制线的“入侵或侵犯”行为。就在几天前，中国军方将阿鲁纳恰尔邦称为“中国领土的固有部分”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:18:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/arunachal-pradesh-part-of-india-us-amid-rising-india-china-tensions/articleshow/108662795.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：中国有望在2027年为入侵台湾做好准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-on-track-to-be-ready-for-taiwan-invasion-by-2027-us/articleshow/108663313.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108663313.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国会议员、官员和军方人士正在就中国国家主席习近平对台湾的意图进行激烈讨论，特别是考虑到他的目标是让中国军队到 2027 年达到“世界一流”地位。约翰·阿奎利诺海军上将指出，这些争论凸显了中国军方对台湾计划的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:06:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-on-track-to-be-ready-for-taiwan-invasion-by-2027-us/articleshow/108663313.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国外交官卢敦促巴基斯坦调查选举，可能重新进行一些投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-diplomat-lu-urges-pakistan-to-probe-election-possibly-re-run-some-votes/articleshow/108662075.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108662075.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国外交官敦促巴基斯坦进行调查，如果证实有干扰，则重新举行大选。人们对暴力和违规行为表示担忧。谢巴兹·谢里夫在选举后领导一个联盟。安东尼奥·古特雷斯也表达了担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-diplomat-lu-urges-pakistan-to-probe-election-possibly-re-run-some-votes/articleshow/108662075.cms</guid></item><item><title>为了减少二氧化碳排放，美国宣布旨在逐步淘汰燃油汽车的规则</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/to-cut-co2-footprint-us-announces-rules-aimed-at-phasing-out-gas-cars/articleshow/108660926.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108660926.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府出台了气候法规，要求到 2032 年大多数美国新车必须是电动汽车或混合动力汽车，这与他减少 50% 排放量的目标保持一致，并带来了显着的社会和经济效益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:52:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/to-cut-co2-footprint-us-announces-rules-aimed-at-phasing-out-gas-cars/articleshow/108660926.cms</guid></item><item><title>沃恩·格辛当选威尔士首席部长，英国首位黑人政府领导人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/vaughan-gething-elected-as-first-minister-of-wales-uks-first-black-govt-leader/articleshow/108661930.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108661930.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;沃恩·格辛（Vaughan Geting）是威尔士第一位黑人领袖，他拥护团结和多样性。在塔塔钢铁公司裁员等挑战中，他的领导目标是引导威尔士度过艰难时期，重点是庆祝差异和团结。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/vaughan-gething-elected-as-first-minister-of-wales-uks-first-black-govt-leader/articleshow/108661930.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡允许外国船只停靠补给</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/lanka-to-let-foreign-ships-dock-for-replenishments/articleshow/108660912.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108660912.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/lanka-to-let-foreign-ships-dock-for-replenishments/articleshow/108660912.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯本周第六次访问以色列</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-to-visit-israel-this-week-his-6th/articleshow/108660780.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108660780.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-to-visit-israel-this-week-his-6th/articleshow/108660780.cms</guid></item><item><title>凯特的阴谋在互联网上爆炸</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-spiracies-explode-on-internet/articleshow/108660651.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108660651.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;凯特·米德尔顿在手术后面临着激烈的猜测，理论家认为她失踪或死亡。不仅如此，互联网侦探还宣称，凯特与母亲和丈夫在车里的照片是另一个没有公主面部痣的女人。未经证实的谣言包括对美术馆的压力、婚姻问题和虚假的出生声明，引发了有关她缺席的阴谋论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-spiracies-explode-on-internet/articleshow/108660651.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦挫败对中巴经济走廊瓜达尔港的袭击，击毙7名武装分子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/militants-storm-gwadar-port-complex/articleshow/108657737.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108657737.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俾路支分裂分子袭击了与中巴经济走廊相连的巴基斯坦瓜达尔港务局大楼。七名袭击者在袭击中丧生。这次袭击针对的是政府办公室和情报机构。这次袭击被视为对中国在该地区投资的回应。被禁的俾路支解放军 (BLA) 的一支敢死队马吉德旅 (Majeed Brigade) 声称对此次袭击负责。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/militants-storm-gwadar-port-complex/articleshow/108657737.cms</guid></item><item><title>德克萨斯州可以在边境逮捕移民吗？反复裁决引发混乱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/can-texas-arrest-migrants-at-border-back-forth-rulings-spark-confusion/articleshow/108660395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108660395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿博特州长的律师和拜登政府在新奥尔良一家法院就备受争议的移民逮捕法发生冲突，导致边境地区混乱，并遭到移民倡导者和墨西哥政府的强烈反对。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/can-texas-arrest-migrants-at-border-back-forth-rulings-spark-confusion/articleshow/108660395.cms</guid></item><item><title>两名巴基斯坦学生因“亵渎”杀害老师而被判处死刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-sentence-2-female-students-to-death-for-killing-teacher-over-alleged-blasphemy/articleshow/108657754.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108657754.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;三名神学院女学生 Razia Hanfi、Ayesha Naumani 和 Umra Aman 因在巴基斯坦西北部谋杀老师 Safoora Bibi 被判亵渎罪。该事件发生在德拉伊斯梅尔汗区的贾米亚伊斯兰法拉胡尔比纳特神学院。两名学生被判处死刑，一名学生被判处无期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-sentence-2-female-students-to-death-for-killing-teacher-over-alleged-blasphemy/articleshow/108657754.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织与巴基斯坦达成11亿美元贷款工作人员级协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/imf-pak-reach-staff-level-agreement-for-release-of-1-1-billion-loan-tranche/articleshow/108657739.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108657739.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦和国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 已达成协议，将发放 11 亿美元，作为 30 亿美元救助计划的一部分。这项财政援助旨在防止巴基斯坦拖欠债务。该协议标志着对巴基斯坦稳定计划的最终审查，并得到了国际货币基金组织团队负责人内森·波特的确认。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/imf-pak-reach-staff-level-agreement-for-release-of-1-1-billion-loan-tranche/articleshow/108657739.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡利斯坦支持者因在英国用基尔潘刺伤3人而被判入狱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/khalistan-supporter-jailed-for-28-months-for-stabbing-three-people-with-kirpan-during-i-day-celebrations-in-southall/articleshow/108657675.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108657675.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 26 岁的卡利斯坦支持者古普雷特·辛格 (Gurpreet Singh) 因去年在索撒尔举行的印度独立日庆祝活动期间用刀刺伤两名印度裔男子和一名女警官而被判处 28 个月监禁。印度公民辛格被发现携带三把刀，其中一把带有20厘米刀片。他还被命令将所有三名柯潘人交给法庭。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/khalistan-supporter-jailed-for-28-months-for-stabbing-three-people-with-kirpan-during-i-day-celebrations-in-southall/articleshow/108657675.cms</guid></item><item><title>法官称，特朗普可以对佐治亚州检察官继续审理此案的裁决提出上诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-can-appeal-ruling-that-kept-georgia-prosecutor-on-case-judge-says/articleshow/108656717.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108656717.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:29:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-can-appeal-ruling-that-kept-georgia-prosecutor-on-case-judge-says/articleshow/108656717.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯别尔哥罗德地区再次受到乌克兰的攻击。为什么总是被针对？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-belgorod-region-is-under-attack-again-from-ukraine-why-does-it-keep-getting-targeted/articleshow/108656644.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108656644.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在莫斯科入侵期间，别尔哥罗德地区面临着乌克兰不断升级的袭击。普京誓言将作出强烈回应，而别尔哥罗德市血腥升级后，官员们加强了防御。该地区拥有重要的铁矿石储量和大型工业企业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:21:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-belgorod-region-is-under-attack-again-from-ukraine-why-does-it-keep-getting-targeted/articleshow/108656644.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示世界必须让全球法治“再次发挥作用”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ukraine-president-zelenskyy-says-world-must-make-global-rule-of-law-work-again/articleshow/108656564.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108656564.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ukraine-president-zelenskyy-says-world-must-make-global-rule-of-law-work-again/articleshow/108656564.cms</guid></item><item><title>饱受危机困扰的海地谈判继续推进</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/talks-push-on-in-crisis-wracked-haiti/articleshow/108656547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108656547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员们表示，在激烈的帮派暴力使海地陷入混乱的背景下，组建治理海地过渡委员会的谈判于周三取得进展。上周亨利同意让位以允许组建临时政府，但尽管面临加勒比邻国和美国的压力，谈判进展缓慢。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:14:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/talks-push-on-in-crisis-wracked-haiti/articleshow/108656547.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>